1
00:01:36,091 --> 00:01:40,091
=Joy of Life Special Edition=

2
00:01:40,091 --> 00:01:43,011
=Episode 6=

3
00:01:43,959 --> 00:01:44,680
Fan.

4
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:48,120
Why are you here today?

5
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,319
I want you to help me with one thing.

6
00:01:49,599 --> 00:01:50,359
What is it?

7
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,000
I want to see the girls in your house.

8
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:54,959
Which one?

9
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:55,359
All of them.

10
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,680
Well.

11
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:01,400
Once I tell you whom she is,

12
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,840
Ruoruo, you go and grab her.

13
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,480
If I do it,

14
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,400
I'm afraid it's a little rude.

15
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,920
Please rest assured.

16
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,719
You will never be ruder.

17
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:19,360
Your Highness, I will get started.

18
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,520
Come and line up.

19
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,719
One by one.

20
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:28,840
Come here.

21
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:33,919
Do you want this one?

22
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,319
This one?

23
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,919
Next. Next.

24
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,479
Next one.

25
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,599
I think this girl is good, brother.

26
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,400
Come one, next one.

27
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,039
Next one.

28
00:02:56,199 --> 00:02:56,599
Come. You can go.

29
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,479
Next one. Next one.

30
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,000
Okay. Next one.

31
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:09,199
Actually, this one is okay.

32
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,919
It must be her.

33
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,159
You haven't found her out?

34
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,080
It's okay.

35
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:23,680
Just wait.

36
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:27,280
The next batch. Come on.

37
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:34,599
You are really picky.

38
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,199
Go. Go. Go.

39
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,159
Don't be afraid. Go. Hurry.

40
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:39,520
Is it her?

41
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,439
Fine. It's not her.

42
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,159
Go. Go. Go.

43
00:03:41,159 --> 00:03:42,080
My brother doesn't want to see you.

44
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:42,639
Please rise.

45
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,080
Haven't you found her?

46
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:46,000
Don't worry.

47
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:47,479
Brother, we still have another batch.

48
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,800
The next batch. Come.

49
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:07,199
They are all here?

50
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:08,520
Yes.

51
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,400
That's impossible.

52
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:15,639
I saw her on the poetry gathering.

53
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:17,759
That day,

54
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:19,279
there were many guests.

55
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:20,959
The maidservant you're looking for

56
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,279
might not be from my mansion.

57
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:24,759
If so,

58
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,839
it won't be easy to find her.

59
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,720
What if I visit all the families

60
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,519
one by one?

61
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,879
I'm afraid
you'll probably be kicked out.

62
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,360
Maybe we should stop.

63
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,240
Actually, there's still another way.

64
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:53,319
But it's much worse.

65
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:55,279
Even worse?

66
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:57,279
Sister, can I go home?

67
00:04:58,399 --> 00:04:58,839
Ruoruo,

68
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,800
do you know Lin Wan'er?

69
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:03,120
I've met her several times
and talked a few words.

70
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:04,040
Where does she live?

71
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:05,759
Sick with tuberculosis,

72
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,240
she stays in an imperial residence
all the year round.

73
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,240
She is the key to this marriage.

74
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,399
Come on!
Let's go to the imperial residence.

75
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,199
Are you going to

76
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:20,720
kill her?

77
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,120
Come with me.

78
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,160
You don't go inside?

79
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,079
I don't.

80
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,639
They are crazy!

81
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:51,399
Lady Ruoruo, wait a moment.

82
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,480
I will go and report.

83
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:53,439
Thank you.

84
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:27,439
Fan Ruoruo has gone to
the imperial residence,

85
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,240
saying she has brought a famous doctor

86
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:31,360
to see Wan'er.

87
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,680
Auntie, why are you smiling so weirdly?

88
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,759
That doctor

89
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:37,720
is Fan Xian.

90
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,120
They're not married yet.
How can they meet in private?

91
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,759
I heard that Fan Xian is
the student of Fei Jie.

92
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:47,240
Those who are good at using poison
are also doctors.

93
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,079
Let them see Wan'er.

94
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:53,720
Auntie,

95
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,800
aren't you against

96
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,040
the marriage all the time?

97
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,120
Fan Xian just left
Prince Jing's mansion,

98
00:07:01,519 --> 00:07:02,800
saying that he wants to
find a maidservant.

99
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,959
A drumstick girl.

100
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:05,800
You heard about it?

101
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,480
A little bird told me.

102
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:12,199
Wan'er doesn't want to marry him.

103
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:14,800
Nor does Fan Xian.

104
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,600
The only person insist on
them getting married

105
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,160
is His Majesty.

106
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:23,560
If Wan'er detests

107
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,959
or even hates Fan Xian,

108
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:30,759
then His Majesty might reconsider it.

109
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:32,879
I see.

110
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,759
By pretending to be a doctor,

111
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,480
Fan Xian wants to piss Wan'er,

112
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,399
so as to ruin the marriage.

113
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:39,839
In this sense,

114
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:42,199
I hope he can succeed.

115
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,639
Do you think he can see Lin Wan'er?

116
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:48,199
A patient suffers from a long illness
certainly wants to see a famous doctor.

117
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,759
Choosing a maidservant

118
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,519
over a princess,

119
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,240
it's not worth it.

120
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:57,519
Indeed.

121
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,759
In this city,

122
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:01,680
only he will make such a choice.

123
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,759
Second Young Master!

124
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,560
Fan Sizhe.

125
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,120
You must be Fan Xian!

126
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,799
Sorry to keep you waiting.

127
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,879
Lady Ruoruo and doctor,

128
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,200
please follow me to see the princess.

129
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:50,200
Lustful, aggressive,
mischievous and ignorant as he is,

130
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:51,919
Wan'er will never marry

131
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:53,000
your incorrigible brother.

132
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,360
Tell Fan Xian.

133
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,720
If he doesn't give up,

134
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,960
this is what he'll become.

135
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:02,759
Who's that?

136
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:06,039
Do you know who Lin Wan'er is?

137
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,840
She's the bastard daughter
of the Princess Royal.

138
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:14,279
Her birth father

139
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,480
is the current Prime Minister Lin Ruofu.

140
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,000
I've also heard that.

141
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,279
The Prime Minister has two sons.

142
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,919
That's Lin Gong,

143
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,840
the Second Young Master of

144
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:24,679
the Lin mansion.

145
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:28,320
So he's the second brother
of Lin Wan'er.

146
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,759
Judged from his attitude,

147
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,639
he doesn't seem to like Fan Xian.

148
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:35,039
That's understandable.

149
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,919
If I were him,
I wouldn't like Fan Xian, either.

150
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,159
Lin Gong

151
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,159
cares for Lin Wan'er

152
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,679
since childhood.

153
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,960
If I were in his shoes,

154
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,240
I wouldn't want my sister

155
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,120
to marry such a troublemaker.

156
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,159
Just think about all the troubles
Fan Xian has caused

157
00:09:47,159 --> 00:09:48,440
since he arrived in the capital city.

158
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,200
To be honest,

159
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,840
if it weren't for the strict rules
of the Lin family,

160
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,639
short-tempered as he is,

161
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:53,639
he might have rushed into

162
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:55,200
our mansion long ago.

163
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:01,639
I've made my point.

164
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:03,759
Just leave!

165
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,759
Second Young Master, I've brought

166
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:10,279
a great doctor

167
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,720
to see Wan'er today.

168
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,200
Wan'er has got tuberculosis.

169
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,240
So many famous doctors
failed to offer a solution.

170
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,080
Young as he is,

171
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,679
how dare you call him great?

172
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,279
What are you doing?

173
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,320
Go away!

174
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,080
Three!

175
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:36,759
Guards!

176
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:38,000
Kick this fraudulent quack

177
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,440
out!

178
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,000
Two!

179
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,360
Ridiculous!

180
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,200
One!

181
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:49,759
I was right!

182
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:51,279
His disease...

183
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:54,519
You... you...

184
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,480
What did you do to me?

185
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,480
Just let me save him first!

186
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,559
His disease...

187
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,960
can't be delayed.

188
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,960
His disease...

189
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,320
His disease...

190
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:06,559
for a long time.

191
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:08,639
Luckily, you meet me today.

192
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,919
It can produce
an excruciating pain in the chest.

193
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,600
Once broke out, it can't be delayed.

194
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,759
Or you'll die.

195
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,279
Take this pill right away!

196
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,440
Young Master, if you don't take it,

197
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,240
you'll die.

198
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,480
It's so effective!

199
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:44,240
What's the name of the disease?

200
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,039
It's called Why Giving Up.

201
00:11:46,799 --> 00:11:47,480
What does it mean?

202
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,320
It means the disease is tricky.

203
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,559
Normally, the cause of the disease
can't be figured out.

204
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:51,799
And eventually,
the patient has to abandon treatment.

205
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,840
Why are you still here! Get out!

206
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,519
Yes!

207
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:01,919
I was wrong.

208
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,840
Master, you're really a great doctor!

209
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:06,039
Will you forgive my ignorance

210
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:07,360
and see my sister?

211
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,759
As doctors, we should be benevolent.
Just lead the way.

212
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,240
I drugged him.

213
00:12:24,399 --> 00:12:25,240
Second Young Master!

214
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:26,240
Lady Wan'er has lied down

215
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,399
as you commanded.

216
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,399
Master, sorry for this.

217
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:32,360
She's unmarried after all.

218
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,759
It's improper for her to show her face.

219
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:36,399
Master, please.

220
00:13:00,279 --> 00:13:01,360
I'm Fan Xian.

221
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,279
I'm here to see

222
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:03,039
what my future wife

223
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:04,639
looks like!

224
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,000
I'm most certain that

225
00:13:17,159 --> 00:13:18,240
by making such a fuss today,

226
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:20,000
you'll have to
let me cancel the marriage!

227
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:22,919
Fan Xian!

228
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,519
Master.

229
00:13:33,519 --> 00:13:35,240
I'm thinking about the disease.

230
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,559
I'll feel her pulse first.

231
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,080
I'm so sorry.

232
00:13:45,759 --> 00:13:47,759
I'm also doing this for your benefit.

233
00:13:48,519 --> 00:13:49,720
Master, sorry to trouble you.

234
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,720
Who... who are you?

235
00:13:54,159 --> 00:13:55,519
Who is your Young Master?

236
00:13:57,759 --> 00:13:59,840
Master, is there anything wrong?

237
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:05,120
To treat the disease,
a guiding drug is needed.

238
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:06,559
What is it?

239
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:09,120
A greasy drumstick
under the censer table

240
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:11,519
in the side palace hall
of the Qing Temple.

241
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:17,399
Such a weird guiding drug.

242
00:15:07,919 --> 00:15:10,080
Why are they still inside?

243
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:19,440
Lin Gong is inside,
and so does Fan Xian.

244
00:15:19,759 --> 00:15:20,720
Will they get into a fight

245
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,399
inside?

246
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,440
What's so good

247
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,440
about girls?

248
00:15:29,759 --> 00:15:32,559
They are talkative and troublesome.

249
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,360
To me,

250
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,399
I might as well count the money!

251
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,840
You're still young.

252
00:15:41,639 --> 00:15:43,200
I'm not!

253
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:44,679
Besides,

254
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,879
it's not relevant.

255
00:15:48,879 --> 00:15:49,679
Why not have a try?

256
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,320
Try talking to a girl?

257
00:16:01,679 --> 00:16:03,200
That one seems nice.

258
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,399
Should I have a try?

259
00:16:06,279 --> 00:16:07,000
She's good.

260
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:14,919
Lady, wait a moment!

261
00:16:15,679 --> 00:16:16,759
Would you like to

262
00:16:17,519 --> 00:16:18,639
play Pai Gow with me?

263
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:19,799
Who are you?

264
00:16:21,279 --> 00:16:24,399
I'm the son of Earl Sinan.

265
00:16:26,919 --> 00:16:27,879
Fan Xian!

266
00:16:30,519 --> 00:16:31,759
If I were Fan Xian,

267
00:16:32,679 --> 00:16:34,399
will you play Pai Gow with me?

268
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,600
Nothing to look at! Let's go!

269
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:10,160
Girls are horrible!

270
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:15,119
What are you doing?

271
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:18,680
I'm seeing the patient.

272
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:19,839
Don't you need to feel her pulse?

273
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,319
Watching her face will do.

274
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:22,599
What do you get?

275
00:17:23,039 --> 00:17:24,440
Does she often cough?

276
00:17:24,759 --> 00:17:25,359
Yes!

277
00:17:25,759 --> 00:17:26,920
Does she pine away day by day?

278
00:17:27,079 --> 00:17:27,599
Right!

279
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,799
Does she often sweat?

280
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:29,640
Right!

281
00:17:29,799 --> 00:17:31,200
Does she often feel a hot flush?

282
00:17:31,519 --> 00:17:33,200
Do you figure that out simply
by watching her face?

283
00:17:33,359 --> 00:17:34,039
Has she coughed blood?

284
00:17:34,119 --> 00:17:34,720
Yes, she has.

285
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:35,559
What's wrong with her?

