couldn't cure me.

741
00:40:26,639 --> 00:40:28,079
That's because they were wrong
from the start.

742
00:40:29,159 --> 00:40:30,599
I didn't ask you to eat more meat

743
00:40:31,039 --> 00:40:31,920
